research_municipality_step.notes: Mount Laurel Township operates under a Faulkner Act Council-Manager (Plan E) form of government. The Township Council consists of 5 members elected at large. The Mayor and Deputy Mayor are selected by the Council from among its members for one-year terms, with Stephen Steglik serving as Mayor and Silvia Catalan-Culnan as Deputy Mayor for 2026.
